Would you like some ice cream ?

28
00:03:14,050 --> 00:03:15,020
Thanks.

29
00:03:15,550 --> 00:03:16,800
Oh, that's right.

30
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:19,050
I don't need to 
thank you today, do I ?

31
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:24,700
Certainly, Miss.

32
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:31,080
I'm glad that you
 actually came today.

33
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,930
As I said, I'm sorry.

34
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:34,690
I just got so engrossed in it.

35
00:03:34,690 --> 00:03:36,200
I'm not mad.

36
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:38,500
I did want to do the folk dance with you, though.

37
00:03:41,210 --> 00:03:44,880
Besides, you're going to 
spend the entire day with me.

38
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:51,100
You're going to pay for everything, 
and you'll do anything I ask, right ?

39
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:56,830
Don't ask for too much.
 I have to pay for all this ?

40
00:03:56,830 --> 00:04:00,130
If a cute girl is asking,
 you should do it.

41
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:02,680
Even if you were cute, 
you're just my kiddy cousin.

42
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:05,900
Hey, that looks so cute.

43
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:06,340
Huh ?

44
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:07,650
Can you buy that for me ?

45
00:04:07,650 --> 00:04:09,210
I just bought you
 a similar one recently.

46
00:04:09,210 --> 00:04:12,000
Why are you looking
 envious, Ryutarou ?

47
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,530
That's silly. 
Why should I be envious ?

48
00:04:14,530 --> 00:04:16,900
You're right.
 You're with me, after all.

49
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:19,000
There's no way you'd
 be envious of anyone.

50
00:04:19,730 --> 00:04:22,580
What ? Why with you ?

51
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:24,000
You're happy, aren't you ?

52
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:24,880


53
